{
  "stem": "11641.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was not death due to violence, as far as I remember correctly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because mostly, we-- mostly were young people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Otherwise, they wouldn't have come there in the first place.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Brunnlitz, they-- when the war came to an end-- was it May 8th-- if I'm not-- not mistaken-- May 8, 1945.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We wake up in the morning one day, and there was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because prior to this-- about two weeks before, we-- there were change of SS completely.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "SS was gone, and the regular German soldiers were there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were old soldiers in the 60s already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were the one who were guiding-- guarding us, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, you know, so this was already all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were not afraid at that time that we'll die, because-- because SS is not there-- unless something unexpectedly will occur.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At-- and when we wake up May the 8th, there was nobody there-- no soldiers-- no Schindler-- and nobody.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were just free-- all of a sudden-- free.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there-- and I remember they were telling me that with Schindler, when someone of the high echelon from our-- this, his closest associate with him-- on the contrary, they should not kill him.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They-- they should be the witnesses what he did for us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they want to go and say, forget about the Russians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Let's go to the American zone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Russians-- they don't care who is who.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So eventually, they reached American zone, and that's how he is alive also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't disappear like Wallenberg by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the first, I remember, came a-- the first allied-- allied soldier, I remember, was a Czech-- Czech partisan girl on a horse.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was a-- she must have been 18 or 19 years old.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
